{"word":"H577 - אָנָּא - ʼânnâʼ - awn-naw' - I beseech thee","slug":"H577","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָנָּא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼânnâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>awn-naw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>I beseech thee"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D0;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05D0; - 'a&#x0302;n'a&#x0302;  'a&#x0302;nna&#x0302;h</b> - <i>awn'-naw, awn'-naw</i><p/>Apparently contracted from <a href=\"#/H160\">H160</a> and <a href=\"#/H4994\">H4994</a>: <i>oh now!</i>: - I (me) beseech (pray) thee, O."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H201\">H201</a>, <a href=\"#/H204\">H204</a>, <a href=\"#/H3982\">H3982</a>, <a href=\"#/H534\">H534</a>, <a href=\"#/H559\">H559</a>, <a href=\"#/H561\">H561</a>, <a href=\"#/H562\">H562</a>, <a href=\"#/H564\">H564</a>, <a href=\"#/H565\">H565</a>, <a href=\"#/H566\">H566</a>, <a href=\"#/H567\">H567</a>, <a href=\"#/H568\">H568</a>, <a href=\"#/H569\">H569</a>, <a href=\"#/H570\">H570</a>"}]}